---
import { ArrowDown, CheckCircle2 } from "lucide-react";
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Thanks | Sawatzky Development"
  description="Thanks for reaching out to Sawatzky Development."
>
  <section class="mx-auto flex min-h-[calc(100dvh-5.5rem)] w-full max-w-2xl items-center px-6 py-10 sm:px-8 sm:py-12 lg:px-10">
    <div
      class="w-full rounded-2xl border border-sky-900/60 bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-900 via-slate-900 to-sky-950/40"
      style="padding: clamp(1.5rem, 3.5vw, 2.25rem);"
    >
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-4 text-center sm:gap-5">
        <div class="inline-flex h-14 w-14 items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-emerald-400/30 bg-emerald-400/10 text-emerald-300 sm:h-16 sm:w-16">
          <CheckCircle2 class="h-7 w-7 sm:h-8 sm:w-8" />
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-balance text-3xl font-semibold text-white sm:text-4xl">Thanks - your message is in.</h1>
        <p class="max-w-xl text-sm leading-relaxed text-zinc-300 sm:text-base">
          I review every inquiry personally and typically reply within one business day with next steps.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="mx-auto mt-6 max-w-xl rounded-xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-950/40 p-4 sm:mt-8 sm:p-5">
        <p class="text-sm font-medium text-zinc-100">While you wait:</p>
        <p class="mt-1.5 text-sm text-zinc-300">Take a quick look at recent work to see style, performance, and structure.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-7 flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-3 sm:mt-9 sm:flex-row">
        <a
          href="/portfolio"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-slate-700 bg-slate-900/40 px-5 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-zinc-200 transition hover:border-sky-500/50 hover:text-white"
        >
          <ArrowDown class="h-4 w-4 text-sky-300" />
          Next step: browse portfolio
        </a>
        <a
          href="/"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md border border-sky-900/60 bg-slate-900/40 px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-100 transition hover:border-sky-500/60 hover:bg-slate-900"
        >
          Back to homepage
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
